ZH: 凡是学习外语的人，都需要投入足够的时间和努力。
EN: Anyone learning a foreign language needs to invest enough time and effort.

ZH: 凡是记住了不同字母的发音规律，发音就会变得更准确。
EN: As long as you remember the pronunciation rules of different letters, your pronunciation will become more accurate.

ZH: 凡是对自己的能力有信心的人，通常能更好地应对挑战。
EN: Those who have confidence in their abilities usually cope with challenges better.

ZH: 凡是我看过的电影，这部是我最喜欢的一部。
EN: Of all the movies I have seen, this is my favorite.

ZH: 凡是我去过的国家，我都留下了美好的回忆。
EN: I have left beautiful memories in every country I have visited.

ZH: 凡是参加演讲比赛的学生，都会获得一份参与证书。
EN: Every student participating in the speech competition will receive a participation certificate.

ZH: 凡是你需要帮助的时候，我都会尽力帮助你。
EN: Whenever you need help, I will do my best to assist you.

ZH: 凡是努力工作的人，都有可能获得成功。
EN: Anyone who works hard has the potential to succeed.

ZH: 凡是违反规定的行为，我们会采取相应的惩罚措施。
EN: Any behavior that violates the regulations will be met with appropriate disciplinary measures.

ZH: 凡是你需要的材料，我都会准备好给你。
EN: I will prepare all the materials you need.

ZH: 凡是具备相关工作经验的应聘者，将被优先考虑。
EN: Candidates with relevant work experience will be given priority consideration.

ZH: 凡是大型活动，都需要提前进行充分的筹备工作。
EN: Adequate preparations need to be made in advance for any large-scale event.

ZH: 凡是世界上的问题，都需要共同努力来解决。
EN: Any problem in the world requires collective effort to solve.

ZH: 凡是经过专业训练的运动员，都具备较高的竞争力。
EN: Athletes who have undergone professional training generally have a higher level of competitiveness.

ZH: 凡是优秀的作品，都展示了作者的独特才华。
EN: Outstanding works always showcase the unique talent of their authors.

ZH: 凡是你说的话，我都会认真听取并进行反思。
EN: I will listen carefully to everything you say and reflect upon it.

ZH: 凡是报名参加比赛的选手，都需要符合相关的报名条件。
EN: Any participant who signs up for the competition needs to meet the relevant registration requirements.

ZH: 凡是遵守交通规则的人，将能够减少交通事故的发生。
EN: People who abide by traffic rules will be able to reduce the occurrence of traffic accidents.

ZH: 凡是优秀的领导者，都能够激发团队成员的潜能。
EN: Excellent leaders have the ability to inspire the potential of team members.

ZH: 凡是合理的建议，我们都会认真考虑并采纳。
EN: We will carefully consider and adopt any reasonable suggestions.

ZH: 凡是按照规定办事的人，都会得到相应的奖励。
EN: People who follow the rules will receive corresponding rewards.
